349
00:19:40.099 --> 00:19:41.099
(CHUCKLES)
JOE GARDNER VÀ NHÓM TỨ TẤU DOROTHEA WILLIAMS

350
00:19:42.269 --> 00:19:44.230
(CHEERS AND APPLAUSE)

