00:20:57.839 --> 00:20:59.380
-Stop fighting this, 22. -22: I don't wanna.
-Đừng kháng cự, 22. -Tôi không muốn.

378
00:20:59.470 --> 00:21:00.509
COUNSELOR JERRY B: You will go to Earth

