Pepperoni.

939
00:44:16.570 --> 00:44:18.739
(JOE AS MR. MITTENS YOWLING)

940
00:44:30.670 --> 00:44:32.090
JOE: Aah, Dorothea Williams saw me.

941
00:44:32.170 --> 00:44:34.219
