01:21:20.960 --> 01:21:22.510
MOONWIND: Joe? JOE: Huh?
Joe?

1689
01:21:23.340 --> 01:21:24.430
MOONWIND: Joe!
Joe!

1690
01:21:24.590 --> 01:21:27.050
