01:22:23.939 --> 01:22:25.069
(RUMBLING)

1707
01:22:27.279 --> 01:22:28.279
JOE: Moonwind!

1708
01:22:28.369 --> 01:22:29.989
MOONWIND: A captain always goes down with the ship.
-Gió Trăng! -Thuyền trưởng phải chìm cùng thuyền.

1709
01:22:30.159 --> 01:22:31.329
It has been a...
Quả là một...

1710
01:22:36.159 --> 01:22:37.170
(SNARLS)

1711
01:22:37.250 --> 01:22:38.250
22!
22!

1712
01:22:39.710 --> 01:22:41.840
Come back, 22. It's me, Joe.
Quay lại đi, 22. Tôi đây, Joe đây.

1713
01:22:44.130 --> 01:22:45.340
Easy, 22, easy.
Bình tĩnh, 22, bình tĩnh.

1714
01:22:45.510 --> 01:22:48.630
